The paper deals with personalized POI recommendation, which is a task related to information retrieval (IR) and social networks (SOC). The proposed method involves matrix factorization (DB) and geographical information (SI), which are also relevant sub-categories. Additionally, the use of a geographical model to improve recommendation accuracy suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (AI) techniques.
